      <item>
        <title>過寶林寺</title>
        <link>https://duoyu.ren/articles/20210716-nanhua-temple/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 16 Jul 2021 23:33:19 +0800</pubDate>
        <author>logos@duoyu.ren (Duōyú Rén)</author>
        <atom:modified>Sun, 02 Oct 2022 23:25:31 +0800</atom:modified>
        <guid>https://duoyu.ren/articles/20210716-nanhua-temple/</guid>
        <description>假期歸鄉，走走停停。時經韶關，暫停二日。老友建議赴丹霞山一遊，吾謂桂林歸來不再遊覽南國山。老友又論證道，桂林山之美，「秀美」也；仁化山之美，</description>
        
