      <item>
        <title>赴粵務工道中謁靖節先生墓</title>
        <link>https://duoyu.ren/articles/20200816-visit-tym-poem/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 16 Aug 2020 13:42:30 +0800</pubDate>
        <author>logos@duoyu.ren (Duōyú Rén)</author>
        <atom:modified>Sun, 02 Oct 2022 21:06:56 +0800</atom:modified>
        <guid>https://duoyu.ren/articles/20200816-visit-tym-poem/</guid>
        <description>盛夏孟秋之日，余自遠方赴粵中務工。時過九江，隨付君小芳謁靖節祠、太白煙、愛蓮池、點將臺、浸水亭。亦談及潯陽三隱、江州司馬、白鹿書院、南山菊茶</description>
        
